flowchart TD
  subgraph UploadFlow[资料上传与解析流程]
    U1[前端上传文件] --> U2[POST /materials]
    U2 --> U3[MaterialService.save -> materials(parse_status=uploaded)]
    U3 --> U4[触发 ParserService 或 POST /materials/{id}/parse]
    U4 --> U5[创建 ai_tasks (parse)]
    U5 --> U6[Worker 执行解析：TXT->parsed_text / PDF|图片->OCR]
    U6 --> U7[更新 materials.parse_status = parsed|failed]
  end

  subgraph AIFlow[AI 闭环]
    A1[用户触发问答/出题] --> A2[检查 materials.parse_status==parsed]
    A2 --> A3[调用 AiService -> external model]
    A3 --> A4[记录 ai_call_logs]
    A4 --> A5[保存 qa_records/questions/test_records]
    A5 --> A6[若答错则写入 wrong_questions]
    A6 --> A7[ReviewPlanService 生成/更新复习计划]
  end
